properties.notes: Demolished in 1910 to make room for the Olympiastadium. The tennis pavilion was dismantled, moved to its current location at Fiskartorpsvägen, and reopened in 1911. In the 1970s, the C-hall was renovated and in 1983 was named a building monument.

properties.notes: The stadium's construction was led by Lennart Hellstedt, brother of Olympian Folke Hellstedt. Olympian William Krigsman worked on the construction of the athletics track.
